<h1>House for Sale in&nbsp;Wildwood Calgary</h1>
<p>Developed in 1956, the established Southwest Calgary real estate community of Wildwood, sits atop a plateau overlooking the Bow River and scenic Edworthy Park.&nbsp; This burgeoning neighbourhood is highly sought after by home buyers because of its large lots with mature trees, gorgeous views and close proximity to the Calgary city core. Homes range from&nbsp;condos and townhomes&nbsp;in the low $200,000&rsquo;s to homes from the mid $450's. Select your price range or specific&nbsp;Wildwood real estate listings below.</p>
